cells.name: Usage
cells.note:
Heatbeat counts per subsystem
=============================

Aggregate heartbeats in a time window set by ``autoInterval`` and count the number of heartbeats in each window.


Select ``Past 7d`` for better visualization. Turn annotations on for a brief description of the relevant events.

from(bucket: "efd/autogen")
  |> range(start: dashboardTime)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r._measurement == "lsst.sal.ATDome.logevent_heartbeat" and (r._field == "heartbeat"))
  |> aggregateWindow(every: autoInterval, fn: count)
  |> keep(columns: ["_time", "_value"])
